    "name": "Hungry Neighbors - A Delicious Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3304060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/db05f7a5c57b3d7d9ebc1f4972d8c847.avif?t=1734044083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras_big/db05f7a5c57b3d7d9ebc1f4972d8c847.avif?t=1734044083 width=800 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/6065ddf28592c959d7dcc3a4b540fcd4.avif?t=1734044083\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turning away from the stress of the big city, you set sail for Horizon Island, a place far from civilisation, where a small community of residents live a simple life in tune with nature. As their new chef, you will ensure that everyone gets fed. It's not so bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Not when there's enough food to go around, at least. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/62f7997a12591c97cae74a592fba9b72.avif?t=1734044083\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This Demo includes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first season of the game, Spring, along with the start of Summer, when all is well on Horizon Island. Roughly a third of a full playthrough, ~60-75 minutes long.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The chance to meet the main cast and start to build those special relationships which will really take you far in life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectible achievements to reward you for replaying the demo, experimenting with different choices and digging for secrets.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Full Game will include:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Routes - each with their own bloody conclusion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The chance to see a whole other side of your new best friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 seasons, each one a little less plentiful than the last.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/4d93099af63d002188384886a0836904.avif?t=1734044083\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get to know your neighbors in a choice-based visual novel format.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/dfe9e029578053a2703454a819a8c403.poster.avif?t=1734044083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/dfe9e029578053a2703454a819a8c403.webm?t=1734044083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/dfe9e029578053a2703454a819a8c403.mp4?t=1734044083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the island in investigation segments.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/d3c157c69e9b8cee7d02284f28ed4f9d.poster.avif?t=1734044083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/d3c157c69e9b8cee7d02284f28ed4f9d.webm?t=1734044083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/d3c157c69e9b8cee7d02284f28ed4f9d.mp4?t=1734044083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare delicious meals with a variety of cooking minigames.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/445d3f390a00043a476c6b6a42ae6a45.poster.avif?t=1734044083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/445d3f390a00043a476c6b6a42ae6a45.webm?t=1734044083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304060/extras/445d3f390a00043a476c6b6a42ae6a45.mp4?t=1734044083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
